divs: Sighting Details AFTER COMING HOME FROM WORK IT IS MY HABITH OF GOING OUT IN MY SMALL TERRACE DURING EVENING ALTOUGHT IN THE CITY IT WAS BRIGHT WATCHING THE BILLBOARD SIGNS ADMIRING THE BUILDINGS LIGHTS. THEN SUDDENLY THERE COME A BLACKOUT WHICH STARTED ABOUT 7PM OUR LOCAL MANILA TIME. FOR ME THAT WAS GREAT FOR I CAN SEE THE STARS MORE CLEARLY. BUT AS I WAS ADMIRING THE SOUTHERN SKY, I SAW THIS SIX CUBELIKE OBJECTS TRAVELLING SLOWLY ( MY ESTIMATE IS THEY MAY BE HIGH AND THEY MAY BE HUGE} TOWARDS THE NORTH ABOVE THE MANILA BAY. I KNOW WHAT AN AIRCRAFT MIGHT LOOK LIKE AT NIGHT AT THIS HEIGHT. BUT ITS DIFFERENT, I TRIED TO TAKE A PHOTO OF THE OBJECTS WITH MY VGA CAM PHONE BUT NO IMAGES CAME OUT. THE LIGHT THE OBJECT EMITTED ARE RATHER PALE.I ONLY LOSE SIGHT OF THE OBJECT WHEN THE POWER RETURNS AND THE SKY WAS AGAIN OBSCURED
Summary: Blue colored cube shaped, 6 in formation.
